title: Person of Interest 3x06 Finch beats Root once more !!!
author: George Finch
comment:
I really love her eyes in this scene. 

And watching this after seeing what a great person she had become at the end almost makes me feel a little empathetic... But it's still hilarious how Root is just speechless after.
little did finch know that if he freed root carter may not have died.
I kind of love Root and her crazy. I probably shouldn't, but she's growing and I like it.
What on Earth is wrong with you people? How can anyone hate Root. She is glorious
